<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于迎来万圣节当天了啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然离晚上5点开始的活动还有一些时间，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我已经按捺不住急切的心情。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经<delay8 />完全是<delay8 />
庆祝万圣节的心情了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />我也一样。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还练习了怎么惊吓大家，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要做好心理准备哦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈哈，<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我开玩笑的啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然准备活动<delay8 />挺不容易的，<delay20 />
不过美好的回忆<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也少不了这部分哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚上5点等了又等的万圣节活动就要开始了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们都要<delay8 />好好享受节日氛围，
把气氛炒热起来啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你为万圣节<delay20 />做足准备了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是还没有的话，你可要抓紧一点啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />5点就要开始了呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">好啦，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多该开始
做乔装打扮的准备了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就期待一下我到底会装扮成什么样子吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会好好<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吓唬吓唬你的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />马上万圣节活动就要开始啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来在活动开始前，<delay8 />
心就是会砰砰跳呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，我看到<tag a="110" b="32" />上<delay8 />摆着
南瓜风格的<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />家具啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也是万圣节的时候了，
多点儿这类装饰<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />的确能有些节日气氛，<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />挺不错的。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，我在<tag a="110" b="32" />上<delay8 />看到了些
南瓜风格的家具，<delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看到了没？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然数量也不是特别多，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但能在身边感受到万圣节的气氛
还是一件开心的事儿啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">关于<tag a="110" b="32" />上的景观我有点话说，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是那些南瓜装饰的事啦，<delay8 />
真有一股万圣节的感觉。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也很期待那一天早点到来。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">这座<tag a="110" b="32" />现在<delay8 />已经被
南瓜的家具堆满了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />简直就像是为了万圣节改造过一样<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这下反倒叫人很期待了，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道当天<delay8 />我们会见识到一个
怎样的万圣节呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>